      "content": "wait, i thought your main priority was keeping the sales velocity up? if we mark them out of stock now, our 'in-stock' metric is gonna tank and the seasonal campaign is basically dead. we'll lose all that momentum. are you sure we can't just keep them listed for a bit longer to ride out the week?",
